Files module
-------------
This module allows to upload and manage files

Methods
-------------

Add file

  url: http://[host]:[port]/[version]/files
  method: POST
  parameters: none, except the multipart file
  
Delete file

  url: http://[host]:[port]/[version]/files/[file id]
  method: DELETE
  parameters: none
  
Get files

    url: http://[host]:[port]/[version]/files
    method: GET
    parameters:
      * page            number of the page, default 1
      * size            number of items per page, default 10
      * fields          fields to retrieve, default all
      * orderby         field to order by, default _id
      * orderdirection  order direction, default asc